<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1325,284,1239]" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">
Remarks. The new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Yang et Saigusa" authorityYear="2001" box="[778,961,1173,1198]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Chrysosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jinpinganum">
<emphasis box="[778,961,1173,1198]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">C. jinpinganum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but can be separated from the latter by the metallic green thorax. In 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Yang et Saigusa" authorityYear="2001" box="[707,889,1213,1238]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Chrysosoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="53" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="jinpinganum">
<emphasis box="[707,889,1213,1238]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="53">C. jinpinganum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the thorax is yellow.
</paragraph>
